### PHONY-3 — Workflow Loader + Config Layer

**Description:**
Implement WORKFLOW.md parsing and the typed config layer with defaults,
$VAR resolution, and path expansion (spec Sections 5.1-5.4, 6.1, 6.3-6.4).

**Proposed Design:**
- src/config/workflowLoader.ts: read file, split --- front matter, parse YAML,
  return WorkflowDefinition. Throw typed errors for missing file, invalid YAML,
  non-map front matter.
- src/config/configLayer.ts: getConfig(raw) -> ServiceConfig. Apply all
  defaults, resolve $VAR in api_key and path fields, expand ~, coerce string
  integers to numbers.
- src/config/validation.ts: validateDispatchConfig(config) -> ValidationResult.
  Checks tracker.kind === "jira", api_key/email/api_token presence, project_key
  present, codex.command non-empty.
- All defaults from src/types/config.ts must be applied when keys are absent.

**Acceptance Criteria:**
- Missing file -> MissingWorkflowFileError
- Invalid YAML -> WorkflowParseError
- Non-map YAML -> WorkflowFrontMatterNotAMapError
- $JIRA_API_TOKEN style env var resolution works
- ~ path expansion works
- All ServiceConfig defaults applied when keys absent
- validateDispatchConfig catches missing required fields
- Jest unit tests covering all error cases and defaults

**Dependencies:** PHONY-1, PHONY-2

